OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry today with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine. A veil of high cloud will
OL,7,Fmove across for a time, making the
OL,8,Fsunshine hazy, but it will still feel
OL,9,Fwarm in the light winds, and clearer
OL,10,Fweather will develop during the
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying dry tonight with
OL,14,Fclear spells, though some cloud
OL,15,Fdeveloping later. Temperatures will
OL,16,Ffall under the cloud breaks to give a
OL,17,Fpatchy rural frost. Milder by the
OL,18,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
