OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,6,Fbe another warm day with light winds.
OL,7,FStaying dry with some bright or sunny
OL,8,Fspells, but cloudier than on Saturday.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,11,FStaying largely dry at the start of
OL,12,Fnext week. Skies will be cloudier at
OL,13,Ftimes, but there will still be some
OL,14,Fwarm sunny spells. Becoming breezy on
OL,15,FWednesday. Chilly nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
